\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\insrsid6313845\charrsid13831242 Stan:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\insrsid6313845\charrsid13831242 Well, I think, obviously, the dominating influence was {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname country-region}}
{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}South Africa{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose} itself. I was growing up in apartheid {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname country-region}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}South Africa{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}
. I was born in 1942, and by the time I\rquote d got ... 
