\rquote s strange, the way in which a child spots ... my mother kept saying, \'93What other lady?\'94 \'93What other lady?\'94 And then when eventually it became clear, I can almost see my mother saying, \'93She\rquote s not a lady\'94, or \'93She\rquote 
