y crude Zionist indoctrination that we received, which I learned later when I went to Israel, how crude it was, and how one-sided it was. But, on the other hand, there was the ... the Zionist }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\f39\insrsid6313845\charrsid11558009 Socialist }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\insrsid6313845\charrsid13831242 side to the Movement. And I unthinkingly absorbed the Zionist side, but the Socialist side of it }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
