And I remember Adam and I being at this meeting, and saying, \'93Well, we can\rquote t just go and celebrate apartheid. We can\rquote t just join in this parade where ... the Afrikaans Youth Movement ...\'94 }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\f39\insrsid11558009 [}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\insrsid6313845\charrsid13831242 a kind of milder Hitler Youth Movement!}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\insrsid11558009 ]}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\insrsid6313845\charrsid13831242 
