rsonal thing, was that he really, I mean, I think if he\rquote d been in Chicago, he would have been a subject of Saul Bellow\rquote s, [}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \i\f39\insrsid6313845\charrsid9847104 Mr Sammler\rquote s Planet}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
