d already felt it, theoretically, because of the reasons I mentioned earlier, about, you know, the realism versus relativism, and those debates
 which were coming. But I felt it, politically, I then, I really began to sense my marginality ... I could see a bit of both sides, and I was never really clearly identifiable by one or other. 
