Well, that was interesting, now the idea came along. Durham had, Durham University had an Extra-Mural Department }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\insrsid11558009 [}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\insrsid6313845\charrsid13831242 don\rquote 
