\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\insrsid6313845\charrsid13831242 Paul:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\insrsid6313845\charrsid13831242 They call it something different.
