\f39\insrsid6313845\charrsid13831242 . He ran the whole of Israeli Sociology like a feudal empire. He actually sent a message to one of his clients to say that, you know, it\rquote s okay if I go into Criminology, but they won\rquote 
t have me in Sociology. Whether it was political, or whether it was because I was doing the kind of sociology they didn\rquote t regard as sociology, I don\rquote t know with their whole setting. I didn\rquote t think it was political, because I wasn
