s where they can help us qualitative people. You know, that we should have something to interpret at least. But we had nothing! And I didn\rquote t have the resources, and figures that I quoted earlier, I managed to p
rise out of a secret market research, they\rquote re very reluctant to give you that information, because information is money for them. And I think it\rquote 
s a very important point to stress, for your methodological interest. We know even less about other fundamental matters \endash  people\rquote s attitude to humanitarian aid, people\rquote 
