The guilt trip is a real concept for people. They feel that they don\rquote t want to be made to feel guilty the whole time. Here\rquote s someone who expresses the guilt paradox beautifully. She said, \'93Well, I watched it, I look at these images ... 
\'94 }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\insrsid11558009 [}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\insrsid6313845\charrsid13831242 on a poster of a child, children trapped in a refugee camp in Bosnia}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\insrsid11558009 ]}{
