15 membership fee, to alleviate that sense of guilt. But it doesn\rquote t work, because when you send the \'a3
15 to Amnesty, they just send you more material. And the more material they send you, you feel more guilty! And so you try and do something about that, then they send you more. It\rquote s never ending!\'94 I mean, I was going to say to he
r, you know, every Jewish ... Jewish first-born child understands, exactly, the problem of guilt, that you have it! And every Catholic understands it, that it\rquote s there. 
