\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\insrsid6313845\charrsid13831242 Stan:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\insrsid6313845\charrsid13831242 Oh, that\rquote s a difficult ... I\rquote d say the worst thing was the ... Oh! I can\rquote 
