\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\insrsid6313845\charrsid13831242 Stan:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\insrsid6313845\charrsid13831242 The worst thing I\rquote 
d say was the consequences of going to Israel, I mean, it was a mistake, and I spent a lot of unhappy time there, hating the place, going, every day, to the campus, and by the time I got there, I\rquote 
d got a migraine headache, and ulcers symptoms! So that was the worst thing. And then, of course, being ill. You know, this was not in my plan. And it is quite an insidious form of illness that creeps over you the whole time, steadily. So that\rquote 
s been the worst thing. Those two, I\rquote d say \endash  going to Israel, and that. 
