The best thing? The best thing has been friends, the quality, the quality of people I know, and the people who, you know, I can turn to and talk to. I don\rquote t like \'93things\'94 \u8722\'2d that includes nature and art }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
